  "text": [
    "I saw a man pursuing the horizon;",
    "Round and round they sped.",
    "I was disturbed at this;",
    "I accosted the man.",
    "\u201cIt is futile,\u201d I said,",
    "\u201cYou can never \u2014\u201d",
    "\u201cYou lie,\u201d he cried,",
    "And ran on."
  ],
  "title": "\"I saw a man pursuing the horizon\"",
  "year": ""
